Revision history for Crypt-DRBG

0.001000 2017-11-20
         * Make Crypt::DRBG::Hash constant time.
         * Mark GitHub as the source for issues.
         * Add support for custom hash functions.

0.000002 2016-02-03
         * Don't call new on Math::BigInt unnecessarily.
         * Fix test failure on old Digest::SHA.
         * Fix breakage on older versions of Math::BigInt.

0.000001 2015-11-28
         * Initial release.
